explanation: [0-0] In an IKEA store, a man in a white hoodie and a man in black clothing stand at the bottom of a staircase with their hands in their pockets, their lower legs illuminated with red light. A woman with purple light stripes on her legs stands on the stairs to the right. A crowd watches, and the beige wall above features green decorations.

[0-8] Next, purple and red light lines illuminate from the feet of the man in the white hoodie and the man in black clothing respectively, converging on their backs to form purple and red patterns. As the patterns disappear, they begin dancing up the stairs. As they dance, purple and red lights illuminate their feet, the lights traveling from their feet up their legs to their backs to form a pattern, then an arrow pointing downwards on their legs. The girl on the stairs dances up and down to the music, the purple light on her legs disappears, and people move around them.
